    title: "Common 11 Plus maths mistakes to avoid.",
    desc: "Master the 11 Plus maths exam by dodging common pitfalls like place value errors, fraction mishaps, percentage blunders, and ratio issues. Learn proven fixes to boost your score and secure success. Start avoiding these traps today.",
    date: "November 5, 2025",
